yōkoso
Welcome to Nakama Anime Bar
Inspired by the streets of Tokyo and popular Anime culture, Nakama is the anime-themed karaoke lounge located in the heart of Orange Park, Florida. Inspired by the enthusiastic community that surrounds the anime world and a shared passion for traditional Japanese karaoke, we decided to combine our passions into one. Having the largest selection of sake in N. Florida, we offer sake cocktails, bottles, flights and bombs, our bar has every thing you need to fuel your encore.
